        "liquid": "<div class=\"ps-testimonials-wrapper\">\n  <div class=\"ps-custom-container\">\n\n    <div class=\"ps-heading-block\">\n      <span class=\"ps-badge\">TRUSTED BY +7000 people</span>\n      <h2 class=\"ps-main-title\">\n        7,000+ people stopped settling for feeling 'off.' <span>Here's what happened.\"</span>\n      </h2>\n      <p class=\"ps-subtitle\">\n        Natural gut support, immune balance & daily wellness — without harsh ingredients.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"ps-custom-grid\">\n\n      <div class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-content\">\n          \"After years of unexplained fatigue and digestive discomfort, I started researching natural anti-parasitic options. Oregano oil and black seed oil kept coming up. Phytoseed Labs combines both at real potency. This is the one that actually worked for me.\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-meta\">Heather D.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-content\">\n          \"I'd returned from travel with persistent gut issues. My naturopath pointed to a potential parasite load. Phytoseed Labs was her exact recommendation. Four weeks later my stool test came back clean and I feel incredible.\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-meta\">Simon R.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-content\">\n          \"My cycle has been more regular since I started. I was diagnosed with PCOS two years ago. My gynecologist recommended I work on inflammation and hormonal balance naturally. After 6 weeks of Phytoseed Labs, my cycle became noticeably more regular and my energy through the luteal phase improved.\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-meta\">Mary B.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-content\">\n          \"I do a seasonal gut detox every year and Phytoseed Labs has replaced my old protocol entirely. The combination of oregano and black seed oil is just more complete — I feel lighter, cleaner, and my skin even cleared up.\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-meta\">Daniel M.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-content\">\n          \"I've had IBS for years and honestly didn't expect much — I've tried everything. Two weeks in, the stomach cramping and rumbling that was basically my daily life has calmed right down. My stomach just feels quieter. Can't explain it but I'll take it.\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-meta\">Camilla H.</div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.ps-testimonials-wrapper{\n  width:100%;\n  padding:80px 0;\n  background:linear-gradient(180deg,#F8F5EF 0%,#F3EEE5 100%);\n  overflow:hidden;\n}\n\n.ps-custom-container{\n  max-width:1250px;\n  margin:0 auto;\n  padding:0 20px;\n}\n\n.ps-heading-block{\n  text-align:center;\n  margin-bottom:50px;\n}\n\n.ps-badge{\n  display:inline-flex;\n  align-items:center;\n  gap:18px;\n  background:#F8F5EF;\n  border:2px solid rgba(201,152,28,0.28);\n  padding:16px 34px;\n  border-radius:999px;\n  font-size:14px;\n  letter-spacing:2px;\n  font-weight:700;\n  color:#4F5F35;\n  margin-bottom:28px;\n  box-shadow:\n    0 8px 30px rgba(201,152,28,0.12),\n    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.9);\n}\n\n.ps-badge::before{\n  content:\"★★★★★\";\n  font-size:30px;\n  letter-spacing:5px;\n  line-height:1;\n  background:linear-gradient(\n    180deg,\n    #FFF8D6 0%,\n    #FFD95A 18%,\n    #F7B500 38%,\n    #D89B00 55%,\n    #B97800 72%,\n    #8F5E00 100%\n  );\n  -webkit-background-clip:text;\n  -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;\n  background-clip:text;\n  filter:\n    drop-shadow(0 2px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.6))\n    drop-shadow(0 4px 12px rgba(247,181,0,0.35));\n  transform:translateY(-1px);\n}\n\n.ps-main-title{\n  font-family:\"Cormorant Garamond\",\"Playfair Display\",serif;\n  font-size:54px;\n  line-height:1.05;\n  color:#2F3527;\n  margin:0;\n  font-weight:600;\n  letter-spacing:-0.5px;\n}\n\n.ps-main-title span{\n  color:#6B7A58;\n}\n\n.ps-subtitle{\n  max-width:760px;\n  margin:20px auto 0;\n  font-size:18px;\n  line-height:1.7;\n  color:#6B7A58;\n}\n\n.ps-custom-grid{\n  display:flex;\n  overflow-x:auto;\n  gap:28px;\n  padding-bottom:22px;\n  scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;\n  -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;\n}\n\n.ps-custom-grid::-webkit-scrollbar{\n  height:6px;\n}\n\n.ps-custom-grid::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{\n  background:#D8C8A2;\n  border-radius:20px;\n}\n\n.ps-review-card{\n  min-width:360px;\n  max-width:360px;\n  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.82);\n  backdrop-filter:blur(8px);\n  border:1px solid #ECE3D5;\n  border-radius:28px;\n  padding:34px;\n  box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);\n  scroll-snap-align:start;\n  transition:all .3s ease;\n}\n\n.ps-review-card:hover{\n  transform:translateY(-4px);\n  box-shadow:0 14px 38px rgba(47,53,39,0.08);\n}\n\n.ps-stars-display{\n  color:#D4AF37;\n  font-size:26px;\n  letter-spacing:5px;\n  margin-bottom:18px;\n  text-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(212,175,55,0.35);\n}\n\n.ps-review-content{\n  color:#2F3527;\n  font-size:16px;\n  line-height:1.85;\n  margin-bottom:24px;\n  font-style:italic;\n}\n\n.ps-review-meta{\n  border-top:1px solid #ECE3D5;\n  padding-top:16px;\n  font-size:13px;\n  font-weight:700;\n  letter-spacing:1px;\n  text-transform:uppercase;\n  color:#6B7A58;\n}\n\n@media(max-width:768px){\n  .ps-testimonials-wrapper{\n    padding:60px 0;\n  }\n\n  .ps-badge{\n    font-size:11px;\n    padding:12px 20px;\n    gap:10px;\n  }\n\n  .ps-badge::before{\n    font-size:22px;\n    letter-spacing:3px;\n  }\n\n  .ps-main-title{\n    font-size:36px;\n  }\n\n  .ps-subtitle{\n    font-size:16px;\n  }\n\n  .ps-review-card{\n    min-width:300px;\n    max-width:300px;\n    padding:28px;\n  }\n}\n</style>",
